description: Deletes the resource policy that is set on a repository. After a resource policy is deleted, the permissions allowed and denied by the deleted policy are removed. The effect of deleting a resource policy might not be immediate.

parameters.name: domain
parameters.description: The name of the domain that contains the repository associated with the resource policy to be deleted.

parameters.name: repository
parameters.description: The name of the repository that is associated with the resource policy to be deleted.

nested_items.name: resourceArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the resource associated with the resource policy.

nested_items.name: revision
nested_items.description: The current revision of the resource policy.

nested_items.name: document
nested_items.description: The resource policy formatted in JSON.
